    "body": "I'm currently running into this issue of the Tor control address not being resolved, as I have set up Tor within a separate Docker container. Unfortunately, this PR doesn't seem to have made it into `22.0`. Does someone know a quick workaround to deal with the dynamically changing IP address, until a `22.1` is released?\r\n\r\nI could go back to managing the hidden service within Tor (and not use a control port) as I have done in the past, but actually I'd prefer to hand over control to bitcoind.",
